sequenceDiagram
    participant Player
    participant PackScreen
    participant SanctuaryService
    participant CollectionService
    participant WriteQueue
    participant Supabase
    participant ObservabilityService

    Player->>PackScreen: Select identified item, tap "Donate"
    PackScreen->>CollectionService: Compute eligible collections
    CollectionService->>CollectionService: species habitats x continents x taxonomicClass

    alt Multiple eligible collections
        CollectionService-->>PackScreen: Multiple collection options
        PackScreen->>Player: Show collection picker
        Player->>PackScreen: Select specific collection
    else Single eligible collection
        CollectionService-->>PackScreen: Single collection_key
    end

    PackScreen->>SanctuaryService: Confirm donation (item_id, collection_key)

    SanctuaryService->>SanctuaryService: Optimistic update: item.status = donated, add to local collection state

    SanctuaryService->>WriteQueue: Enqueue {action: donate, item_id, collection_key}
    WriteQueue->>Supabase: INSERT v3_sanctuary_donations
    WriteQueue->>Supabase: UPDATE v3_items SET status='donated'

    Supabase-->>WriteQueue: Confirm
    WriteQueue->>WriteQueue: Mark CONFIRMED

    opt Collection newly unlocked
        WriteQueue->>ObservabilityService: Log sanctuary.collection_unlocked
    end

    WriteQueue->>ObservabilityService: Log sanctuary.donation

    SanctuaryService->>PackScreen: Item permanently removed from active pack
    Note over PackScreen: Item visible in sanctuary view
